            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix </strong>in 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [200ml]</span> of the <strong>reserved</strong> <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>stock</strong> to the pan and reduce the heat to medium-high, then cook for a further 6-8 min or until the liquid has reduced by half and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1599839000130-x200.jpg",
