      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> drained</strong> <strong>spaghetti</strong> to the pan</p><p>Tip: Stir very thoroughly as this will release the starch in the pasta and make the sauce naturally creamy</p><p>Before the liquid has fully reduced, remove the spaghetti from the heat and stir in your<strong> soft cheese </strong>– this is your <strong>smoky chicken & mushroom spaghetti</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
